Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.19,0:00:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Riki is sleeping right in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.11,0:00:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is such a wonderful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafuu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.64,0:01:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, calm down! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.14,0:01:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why are Riki and I sleeping in the same bed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.23,0:01:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... be gentle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.45,0:01:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As your girlfriend, I'm elated that you'd risk your wellbeing by sneaking into the girls' dorm for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am not quite prepared for all this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.58,0:01:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Y-You don't remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.04,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have we crossed that line already?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.76,0:01:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't remember why I stayed the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, a home run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.44,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That puts us five points ahead! No way they're catching up now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The ball's gone quite far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.11,0:02:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice home run there, Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.82,0:02:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw that, Riki? That's out-of-the-park muscles for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.74,0:02:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Muscles yay yaaay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.37,0:02:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Muscles, muscles!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Muscles yay yaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.79,0:02:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently the boys' dorm was flooded by a water pipe that was damaged by a stray baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.51,0:02:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Who would do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It was yoooou!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.47,Alt,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorryyyy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.14,0:02:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we sleep now...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanata-san, what will the boys do during summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as this goes, we can't really tell them to sleep in the classrooms or the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have the boys stay in the empty rooms in the girls' dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.12,0:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhhh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll assign the rooms by lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No. 4! Who's got No. 4?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be Riki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does my lot say "Rin"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.05,0:03:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the seed, Natsume-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't be bad to spend some family time with your sister during the break now, would it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Sounds like a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.15,0:03:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai, what does "better luck next time" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Naoe-kun, you drew that one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't actually have enough empty rooms left in the girls' dorm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.83,0:03:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be staying in the home economics clubroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.09,0:03:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to stay in the clubroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I drew the bad lot, so it seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...looking for a roommate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's why...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.00,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to be my roommate?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, but a girl and boy staying in the same room...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If siblings are fine, I don't see a problem if a girlfriend and boyfriend share a room, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.48,0:04:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Riki is so rational.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.45,0:05:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That was actually just an excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth, I just want to spend more time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that not okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's how we ended up staying in your room together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That rings a bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did we end up sleeping in the same bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.59,0:05:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka, what was that scream just now about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,K-K-Kanata-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm changing right now, so wait just a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka, why are you answering the door wearing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feel bad to keep you waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Eek!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm changing right now...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Could you please come back later...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.58,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are guys staying in the dorms now, so think about the way you dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a guy in this room right now, not just the dorms!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's okay! Riki isn't in the room right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course he isn't. What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if Riki was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All the guys staying in the girls' dorm would have to take collective responsibility and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd have to sleep in the classrooms for the summer instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you ask something like that, Kudryavka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Because Riki... isn't here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course he isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now hurry up and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't bring much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer, so I don't have to worry about bulky clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should I put my underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can put them in the top drawe —
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up, Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafuuuu!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not thinking anything like, "I didn't expect them to be so small" or "You've got some pretty mature stuff in here"!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka-kun, may I have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurugaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there something you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. I'm here to return the panties I borrowed when I visited the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you borrow those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Kurugaya-san, what are you doing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.48,0:07:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm putting them back where I got them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, it's summer all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.01,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been caught...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sure Kurugaya-san will keep it a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuu-chan, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Komari-san, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when I came to hang out the other day — waah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess it's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamikita-san found out, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine! I'm sure it's all going to be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:08:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is summer, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, let's go get breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good! We won't have to hide anything with everyone there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.69,0:09:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My my, summer's in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.75,0:09:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you been lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.46,0:09:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you miss my muscles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.54,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts, Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, you can come stay in our room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have our muscles futon laid out and ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,With Kengo on the bottom, me on top,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and you right in the middle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.22,0:09:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please elaborate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you're worried about your childhood friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.35,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it's senseless of you to make light of his determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, more so than anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.49,0:09:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, it's summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's senseless because it's summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That seems to be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.80,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pokey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you baldy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigusa-san, is that a new prank of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.31,0:10:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a static generator for my research project!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, so it's a prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's science!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, we need to work on our independent research.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Masato?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A growth record of my muscles, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.91,0:10:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make it sound like you're recording the growth rate of morning glories...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Kud?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.46,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a rocket, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryachka, been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see, Himuro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Himuro-san. She's visiting from our sister school during the summer for her research.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Yuuki Himuro, president of the sister school's science club.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she was my roommate while I was in Tevua!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's quite the interesting project you're working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My summer research project is going to be on water rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make this yourself, Kuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've made one,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's probably lots of room for improvement!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we just need to use this to pump in air.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.16,0:12:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't we just use a compressor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's getting... harder and harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like doing isometrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.71,0:12:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Inohara-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks to be ready for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,On the launch, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,T-minus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing, Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It flew that far with just water and air!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.08,0:12:50.00,Alt,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This was nothing more than craftwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.75,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to record data and keep experimenting to make it go further.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.80,0:13:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you should start with the wings' shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you shape them like screws,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.35,0:13:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make the rocket spin, which will stabilize its trajectory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A rocket launching into the blue summer sky, soaring among white clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.86,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all launch our own water rockets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who emerges victorious in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...will be given the title "Rocket King"!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mission start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock, paper, scissors!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Noooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Wooow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so good at this, Haru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.59,0:13:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-chan, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop complaining and get a move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Waaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.98,0:13:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My rockets!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.49,0:14:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoh! Hah! Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you won't drop them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned rockets just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you making water rockets with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.10,0:14:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,How'd you know, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, we're actually going to make rockets ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You must all be really good friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.32,0:14:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have friends like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,so I have to make them by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Noumi Kudryavka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.33,0:15:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina... Arizuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina-san, we're friends now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's up to you, but would you like to make water rockets with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.61,0:15:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our welcome cookies for Himuro-san and Shiina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I eat these?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This many will be a total cakewalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all soda, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kengo, let's see which of us can down more of these!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.75,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems it's time for me to put you in your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Aghhh! My eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyeeeeeees!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You brought that on yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, let's all make rockets out of the empty bottles!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Would shaping carbon nanotube like a bottle be cheating?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Carbon nanotube?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.47,0:16:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You make real rockets with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Real rockets?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.47,0:16:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.56,0:16:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiina-san, why do you want to make water rockets?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to become an astronaut!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My dream's to become a kosmonavt, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, my mother is a kosmonavt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in the International Space Station right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get back to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, who's going to launch theirs first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.31,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This rocket was jointly developed by Anego and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.18,0:17:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Sexy Anego!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a picture on the rocket,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but this doesn't have anything to do with Kamikita-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's one of my most prized photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to see Komari-kun in quite the embarrassing situation when the rocket is launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhh?! When did you take such a picture?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.95,0:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huu! Huu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.04,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Masato!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.21,0:17:44.54,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wait up...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, with how far it's flown, I can't see\NKomari-kun's unbecoming appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.22,0:17:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Strelka, don't fetch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.31,0:17:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, here's the Naoe, made by Komari-san and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Inohara-san, if you would, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.32,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Once it is launched, the photos of Naoe-san and Kyousuke-san will turn into ones where they're hugging each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ehhhh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:15.95,Alt,,0,0,0,,Wafu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.95,0:18:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I shopped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.70,0:18:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.96,0:18:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Belka, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It went farther than the Saigusa-Kurugaya team's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.05,0:18:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:37.60,Alt,,0,0,0,,Fungaaaargh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to launch them with water and air...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that's against the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.98,0:18:46.98,Alt,,0,0,0,,No waaaaaay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.36,0:18:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Pwapapopopeh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we have to use water and air?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.41,0:19:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Next up, it's Riki, Noumi, and Shiina!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Okay! Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.01,0:19:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud-san, can I become an astronaut?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming a kosmonavt is a big dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.44,0:19:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But as long as you don't give up, you'll get there for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.20,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I believe so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, it's all done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,On the launch, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.13,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,5!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.59,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,4!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,3!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,2!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.47,0:20:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,1!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.39,0:20:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.95,0:21:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,When it comes to finding Polaris, my mom is a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.12,0:21:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd start from the Summer Triangle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.58,0:21:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put Altair of Aquila on the other side of the line connecting Vega of Lyra and Deneb of Cygnus,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.29,0:21:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that's where you'll find Polaris.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.30,0:22:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been looking at me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.05,0:22:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about how much you love your mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.86,0:22:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.20,0:22:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, could you listen to me for a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.66,0:22:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.37,0:22:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom is a really amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I admired her... and she was my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My mom has been a kosmonavt for as long as I can remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.97,0:22:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and she has always cheerfully told me{\i0} {\i1}the importance of going into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reason I wanted to go to space...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.19,0:23:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The reason I wanted to become a kosmonavt was because{\i0}\N{\i1}I wanted to see the same things my mom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to find out that the things she said{\i0} {\i1}she enjoyed are actually fun myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That was my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.25,0:23:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that was a really difficult road to follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.88,0:23:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The further I went, the farther away it felt like my mom was.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before I knew it, I had stopped in my tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.56,0:23:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I ran away from my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I didn't have the confidence to fulfill her{\i0} {\i1}expectations and ran away from Tevua.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just that, a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to keep at it and become a kosmonavt, thinking that would somehow justify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.96,0:24:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think being able to talk to someone about your dreams is pretty impressive on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.13,0:24:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes me want to keep cheering you on by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.14,0:24:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.77,0:24:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... is it okay if I cast a good-luck charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.07,0:24:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.66,0:24:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a charm for tying people who treasure each other together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.99,0:24:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We draw our coat of arms on each other, and they turn into stronger bonds and oaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.84,0:24:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.39,0:24:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is very embarrassing... and also very important and serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.40,0:25:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.27,0:25:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ma-Marry?! Like tying the knot?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.44,0:25:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still in school, so I'm not trying to ask for something that ambitious yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.07,0:25:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have about the same determination and resolve...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.20,0:25:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.12,0:25:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.80,0:25:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.51,0:25:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.26,0:25:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.43,0:25:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.06,0:25:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,My coat of arms is filled with curvy waves and mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.65,0:25:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom told me they were gears.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.82,0:25:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gears?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.16,0:25:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a good set of gears to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.87,0:26:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.17,0:26:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.21,0:26:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.42,0:26:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very... sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.22,0:26:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.31,0:26:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.27,0:26:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It tickles...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.94,0:26:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of pattern are you drawing on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.11,0:26:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Trees, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.40,0:26:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll always be there around you, protecting you from all sorts of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.67,0:26:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.69,0:27:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be able to do anything as long as Riki's with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.07,0:27:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as Riki is there, that's where I belong...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.15,0:27:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...no matter where...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.95,0:27:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kud, wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.00,0:27:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.63,0:27:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... Kud...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.51,0:27:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Even in your dream, you're there right next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.13,0:29:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Riki's sleeping right in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.05,0:29:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is such a wonderful dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.65,0:29:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kud.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.07,0:30:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Riki.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.00,0:30:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.75,0:30:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.55,0:30:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, everyone went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.55,0:30:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.56,0:30:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...alone with Riki this entire summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.19,0:30:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, let's go get breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.70,0:30:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, the cafeteria staff aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.08,0:30:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't I make breakfast for you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.75,0:30:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.58,0:30:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.46,0:30:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come get you once I'm done, so just hang around in my room until then!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.27,0:31:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... wafu.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.48,0:31:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm making miso soup for Riki...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.57,0:31:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like we're newlyweds!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.21,0:31:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to keep running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.89,0:31:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Himuro-san, you're a strong person,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.18,0:31:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so there's no way you'll understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.35,0:31:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to be strong, nothing more,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.27,0:32:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just come off as strong to you as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.90,0:32:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why, for how strong I am, I can remain here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.61,0:32:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've noticed, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.03,0:32:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That this place is closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.50,0:32:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Still going to repeat it all?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.54,0:32:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke-san said something similar...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.92,0:32:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And now... Himuro-san... you're telling me the same thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.22,0:32:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It just means you want someone to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.22,0:32:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as Riki's with me, I don't need anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.60,0:32:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.48,0:32:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as Riki's with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.40,0:32:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as he's there...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.66,0:32:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, breakfast's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.66,0:32:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.96,0:33:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki! Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.50,0:33:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.42,0:33:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.76,0:33:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.01,0:33:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.57,0:33:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.95,0:33:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always known...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.91,0:33:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a convenient world where everything works out.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.71,0:33:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A misguided paradise that I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.59,0:33:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to become stronger, even if just within this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.55,0:33:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could get just a little better... become just a bit stronger...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.98,0:34:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...perhaps I could take flight one day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.61,0:34:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No... I'm sure that won't ever happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.07,0:34:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll only ever be like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.11,0:34:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud...!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.49,0:34:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.20,0:34:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.50,0:34:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come help you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.01,0:34:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.47,0:34:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get these chains off right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.56,0:34:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki! Please stop...!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.98,0:34:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.31,0:34:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember everything... I know what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.42,0:35:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already given up because of the accident on the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.88,0:35:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a relief to have it all come to an end even if I didn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.01,0:35:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted you, whom I love the most, to be saved,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.43,0:35:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so I prayed over and over...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.89,0:35:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, just knowing you got out fine was more than enough for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.48,0:35:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not fine with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.82,0:35:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We were going to rescue everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.66,0:35:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud... I wanted to become someone who's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.29,0:35:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to understand what it meant to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.71,0:35:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted the strength to protect somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.21,0:35:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And... I learned from everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.26,0:35:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I learned what it meant from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.47,0:36:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was able to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.31,0:36:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... not strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.48,0:36:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I repeated all of this over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.90,0:36:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept repeating everything over and over and over because it worked out for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.66,0:36:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...and kept running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.91,0:36:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll repeat it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.58,0:36:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm weak. I'll only ever be bound by these chains...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.04,0:36:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only ever be a Kudryavka who can't take flight.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.92,0:36:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.46,0:36:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been looking for a way to get stronger this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.64,0:36:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.35,0:36:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. You already know what that means.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.69,0:36:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I already do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.48,0:36:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.54,0:37:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.63,0:37:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You can fly anywhere as long as you wish for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.30,0:37:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feelings will reach anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.14,0:37:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuu-chan, I've filled it up with water!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.47,0:37:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Komari-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.39,0:37:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all set and ready to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.89,0:37:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nishizono-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.56,0:37:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can count on our calculations for the wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.73,0:37:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The wind's calm. It's the perfect time for launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.35,0:37:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Saigusa-san! Kurugaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.40,0:37:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Inohara-san! Miyazawa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.53,0:37:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving the rest to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.74,0:37:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Just ten more pumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.74,0:37:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Noumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.95,0:37:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a new mission for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.83,0:37:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Surpass yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.17,0:37:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.42,0:37:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.75,0:37:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyousuke-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.96,0:37:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Rin-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.93,0:38:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.01,0:38:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The mission's started!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.43,0:38:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.93,0:38:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,10... 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.06,0:38:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,8... 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.23,0:38:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,6...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.03,0:38:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been running away this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.32,0:38:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really get any stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.95,0:38:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,5...!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.16,0:38:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All you've been doing is repeating this comfy world of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.41,0:38:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,4...!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.96,0:38:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You, the Kudryavka who's bound by chains and cannot fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.63,0:38:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to get stronger! I want to fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.51,0:38:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to do it, stick it out to the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.18,0:38:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't just have all the fun yourself. Let me join in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.10,0:38:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryachka, believe in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.90,0:38:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Himuro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.07,0:39:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Himuro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.61,0:39:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't give up, your wish will surely come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.45,0:39:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.29,0:39:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,3...!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.58,0:39:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,2...!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.75,0:39:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.59,0:39:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.97,0:39:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.85,0:39:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.35,0:39:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.00,0:39:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.55,0:40:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,1...!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.73,0:40:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.73,0:40:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.23,0:40:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.11,0:40:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.98,0:40:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get stronger by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.65,0:40:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fly if you aren't there next to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.70,0:40:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.33,0:40:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kud...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.71,0:40:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.58,0:40:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.05,0:40:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ri...ki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.93,0:40:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Riki on the other side of the sky...?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.01,0:40:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he been watching over me this whole time...?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.73,0:41:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right... Riki and I are connected.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.91,0:41:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki... I'm coming to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.20,0:41:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,On the launch, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.37,0:41:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Starting countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.79,0:41:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,T-minus
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.21,0:41:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}9, 8, 7, 6, 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.75,0:41:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Those chains represent my weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.67,0:41:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The weakness of seeking strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.05,0:41:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They may appear to be connections, but they're actually rejections.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.80,0:41:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have friends who are there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.39,0:41:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whenever I'm feeling lonely or in trouble, they're always there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.81,0:41:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And Riki has always been there to support me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.57,0:41:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,2! 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.82,0:41:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignition!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.64,0:42:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.94,0:42:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.48,0:42:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.02,0:42:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Kuu-chan wake up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.40,0:42:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Little Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.94,0:42:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.15,0:42:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Kudryavka-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.40,0:42:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Noumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.07,0:42:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.82,0:42:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Noumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.17,0:42:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Kud.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.10,0:43:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.35,0:43:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.35,0:43:01.31,Alt,,0,0,0,,Kud!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.31,0:43:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurray! Hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.10,0:43:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After that long, long dream, I finally managed to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.65,0:43:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to save Riki, but he saved me in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.42,0:43:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I never knew about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.76,0:43:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew I wanted to come here with you as soon as I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.26,0:43:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see all kinds of stars here when it gets dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.39,0:43:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, would you like to come stargazing some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.94,0:43:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'd love to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.77,0:43:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki, would you mind listening to me about two things?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.65,0:43:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Two things?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.82,0:43:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is a question I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.99,0:44:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think strength actually is?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.37,0:44:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you've already found that answer yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.12,0:44:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't quite understand it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.42,0:44:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're strong just because you're not weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.55,0:44:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's just understanding what it means to be weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.85,0:44:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wafu...?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.43,0:44:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the ability to acknowledge you are weak and take even just one step further.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.06,0:44:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I think it means to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.73,0:44:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.65,0:44:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,How philosophical.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.78,0:44:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hehe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.53,0:44:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the other thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.99,0:44:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The second thing is something I wanted to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.75,0:44:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work hard to become a kosmonavt.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.71,0:44:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think there's going to be a tough road ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.92,0:44:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am bound to lose heart over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.92,0:45:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but I still want to make that my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.89,0:45:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've made your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.43,0:45:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.06,0:45:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.64,0:45:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay if I add just one more thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.82,0:45:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Riki...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.66,0:45:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you!
